<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Protoconch sculpture of Alycaeus Gray, 1850 species A Alycaeus eydouxi Venmans, 1956 (Cochinchina, coll. V. W. MacAndrew, NHMUK) B Alycaeus rolfbrandti Maassen, 2006 (MNHN-IM- 2012 - 27321) C Alycaeus conformis Fulton, 1902 (HNHM 99714, spec 3). Scale bars: 1 mm. All images: Barna Pall-Gergely." , "Figure 1. Traits of alycaeid protoconch A, B smooth: Dicharax cristatus (Moellendorff, 1886) (2010.05.08 A, coll. PGB) C, D pitted. C: Chamalycaeus sculptilis (Benson, 1856) (NHMW 71770 / R / 17); D: Dicharax itonis (Kuroda, 1943) (NSMT 78866) E, F spirally striated: Metalycaeus muciferus (Heude, 1885) (2013 / 7, coll. PGB). All images: Barna Pall-Gergely." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/468647" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/468646" .

